data.description: Welcome home to this delightful Lakeview Cove condo, tucked away in Smithfield, VA!  This beautifully designed corner unit boasts 3 stories, flooded with natural light, and soaring vaulted ceilings.  The kitchen features custom cabinetry and a pantry for ample storage, and stainless steel appliances. Adjacent laundry room provides additional storage.  Living Room with gas burning fireplace, and surround sound.  The generous primary suite offers a walk-in closet, reading nook, and bath with double sinks, separate shower, and large soaking tub.  Enjoy sunsets and grow your own herbs on the 2nd storey covered balcony.  3rd Floor loft.  3 Car garage.  Community Pool and Clubhouse.  Conveniently located 5 minutes from grocery shopping, and the many shops and restaurants of charming downtown Smithfield!
